            <span style="color:#FF0000;font-size:larger;"><b>TMI Tutorials Must Be Managed Through Blogger</b></span><br/><br/>
			Unlike most other data on TMI, we do not store and manage Tutorials: each tutorial
			is just a post on this <a href=http://tmitutorials.blogspot.com/>Blogger blog</a>.<br/><br/>
			TMI's Tutorials page simply grabs links to those posts, and embeds their content in
			the TMI layout when clicked.<br/><br/>
			Thus, to add/edit/delete Tutorials, login to Blogger and manage posts.<br/><br/>
